<h1 id="prod_diagnostics_top"><a href="#prod_diagnostics_top">Docker Production Container Build Failure Diagnostic Report</a></h1>

<div class="toc" id="toc">
<h3>Quick Navigation</h3>
<ul>
    <li><a href="#problem_statement">Problem Statement</a></li>
    <li><a href="#root_cause">Root Cause Analysis</a></li>
    <li><a href="#technical_details">Technical Details</a></li>
